{"tid":644782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個親眼目睹人自殺/意外死既經歷","createTime":"2018-04-27T13:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T03:22:44.000Z","uid":36097,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ece7d80cef4ed4d18995b4e9fed26425585ff543","tid":644782,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"見過6次， 雖然唔係全部自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第1次係好細過9 點鐘到去左買包， 有個人跳樓， 落點係我前面2,30 米.... 但個陣唔知點解唔驚， 我仲記得佢個頭撞落平台再彈落地下<br />\n<br />\n第2 次係之前有個差佬係長沙灣比人斬中大動脈....... <br />\n<br />\n第3 次係意外黎， 係太子補完習， 有個伯伯係唐樓唔知邊層跳落黎....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個頭好似扑西瓜咁爆開左<br />\n<br />\n第4 次係中學同學比車撞， 望住佢離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第5 次係老豆心臟病.... 個日?醫生護士問我同唔同意唔再維持生命機能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第6次係polyu hall有氧跳樓， 咁岩我行到對面,已經冇乜感覺了。"},{"pid":"1672c6f2cc2a1ecf67953afb5558d049ff94f6e4","tid":644782,"uid":36097,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"大家一定要珍惜生命,自殺真係太恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3f043942ef704b71c9b8e5ed7a93bdbf3bd5c6","tid":644782,"uid":9732,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21057b54d0f155e764d33e4d24b4efc95acb4589","tid":644782,"uid":50060,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:28:40.000Z","msg":"樓主係真人版柯南？<br />\n你係邊區翻學/做野，我盡量唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f29fcfcb03ac784042b8da022631970339282d8","tid":644782,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21057b54d0f155e764d33e4d24b4efc95acb4589","tid":644782,"uid":50060,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"cit